is backend saw delay spikes from ~1771 ms to over 24676 ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"GetQuote operation latency increased from ~205 ms to 909 ms.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThe identified components exhibited significant performance degradation, suggesting that the issue involves severe latency variations impacting both storage access and internal service operations, particularly within the checkout and product catalog paths impacting overall processing time."}
